
Simple program to "play" with GPU

LIMITATION
At the moment works only with NVIDIA GPUs

* checkGPU: cudafortran program, it perform a simple query to understand the main features of the GPU

[gamati01@lrdn2525 CHECK_GPU]$ ./a.out 
